WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.166 --> 00:00:03.166
Why did you beat the horse with that waiter?

2
00:00:03.166 --> 00:00:06.066
It's not that he was kidnapped

3
00:00:06.300 --> 00:00:07.766
Qin Changan saved him

4
00:00:07.766 --> 00:00:09.500
He is ungrateful and blames others

5
00:00:09.500 --> 00:00:11.733
And find someone to plot against me

6
00:00:11.733 --> 00:00:12.933
You bloody official

7
00:00:12.933 --> 00:00:14.466
It was obviously you who beat Qin Changan

8
00:00:14.466 --> 00:00:16.866
I dare to fight

9
00:00:16.866 --> 00:00:19.366
If you don't give me an explanation today

10
00:00:19.533 --> 00:00:22.000
I asked the old man to hold a family meeting

11
00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:23.500
Drive you out of the territory

12
00:00:23.700 --> 00:00:26.766
Why don't you hurry up and hand over that floating life to me?

13
00:00:26.766 --> 00:00:28.300
I'm telling the truth.

14
00:00:28.466 --> 00:00:29.800
Why do you believe what he says?

15
00:00:29.800 --> 00:00:31.333
You don't listen to what I say

16
00:00:31.333 --> 00:00:32.566
Why do you say

17
00:00:32.666 --> 00:00:35.533
Our Wan'er thinks of the Lin family everywhere

18
00:00:35.533 --> 00:00:36.666
What about you?

19
00:00:36.800 --> 00:00:39.866
What did you do when the Lin family needed you?

20
00:00:39.933 --> 00:00:42.633
You don't deserve to be a member of the Lin family

21
00:00:42.733 --> 00:00:43.766
That is.

22
00:00:43.866 --> 00:00:46.666
Let you marry Sun Shao and save the Lin family, you don't even recognize it

23
00:00:46.666 --> 00:00:48.766
What else have you done to the Lin family?

24
00:00:48.900 --> 00:00:49.933
Go away by yourself

25
00:00:49.933 --> 00:00:50.800
Lin Jinhan

26
00:00:51.400 --> 00:00:52.833
This is your daughter.

27
00:00:52.900 --> 00:00:54.000
Make a statement

28
00:00:54.300 --> 00:00:57.466
Well, I'll give you another chance.

29
00:00:57.666 --> 00:01:00.233
Do you want to hand over that goddess?

30
00:01:00.266 --> 00:01:03.466
If not, don't blame me for not recognizing you as a daughter

31
00:01:03.700 --> 00:01:06.166
I said it was right.

32
00:01:06.166 --> 00:01:07.466
Then get out of here

33
00:01:07.466 --> 00:01:09.000
Who dares to let him go

